#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour412.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.12 tour"
msgstr "Tur Xfce 4.12"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to new major features of Xfce 4.12. It only covers improvements made on the surface; for the full list of changes, see the [changelogs](/download/changelogs/).\n"
msgstr "Tur ini akan memperkenalkan Anda kepada fitur-fitur utama yang baru di Xfce-4.12. Ini hanya meliputi peningkatan yang dibuat di permukaan; untuk daftar lengkap perubahan, lihat [log perubahan](/download/changelogs/).\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window Switcher Dialog"
msgstr "Dialog Penukar Jendela"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "The window manager's Alt+Tab dialog is now fully themeable and also gained two new modes: a 'List' mode and a 'Window Preview' mode. Furthermore users use their mouse to click/select the window they want to give focus to.\n"
msgstr "Dialog Alt+Tab manajer jendela sekarang bisa menggunakan tema sepenuhnya dan juga mendapatkan dua mode baru: mode 'Daftar' dan mode 'Pratinjau Jendela'. Selain itu pengguna bisa menggunakan tetikus untuk memilih jendela yang akan diberi fokus.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The traditional dialog is fully themable now][img-tabwin-simple-crop]\n"
msgstr "![Dialog tradisional sekarang bisa menggunakan tema sepenuhnya][img-tabwin-simple-crop]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "The List mode of the Alt-Tab dialog.\n"
msgstr "Mode Daftar dialog Alt-Tab.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "![List mode of Alt-Tab, showing all window titles][img-tabwin-list-crop]\n"
msgstr "![Mode Daftar Alt-Tab, menampilkan semua judul jendela][img-tabwin-list-crop]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Window Preview mode shows thumbnails of windows' content alongside their icon. Activating the compositor is a prerequisite for this mode.\n"
msgstr "Mode Pratinjau Jendela menampilkan miniatur isi jendela di samping ikon. Mengaktifkan kompositor menjadi prasyarat mode ini.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Window thumbnails][img-tabwin-preview-crop]\n"
msgstr "![Miniatur jendela][img-tabwin-preview-crop]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:25
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tiling, Zooming, Client-side Decorations"
msgstr "Dekorasi jendela sisi klien"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "Support for Client-Side Decorations (CSDs) has been improved. They now properly snap to screen and panel borders, and tile correctly, even with shadows.\n"
msgstr "Dukungan untuk Dekorasi Sisi-Klien (CSD) telah ditingkatkan. Kini mereka bisa melekat ke tepi layar dan panel dengan baik, dan diubinkan dengan benar, bahkan dengan bayangan.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Gtk3 apps with their decorations drawn by the client][img-xfwm4-csd]\n"
msgstr "![Aplikasi Gtk3 dengan dekorasinya digambar oleh klien][img-xfwm4-csd]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window tiling mode was improved by providing support for corner-tiling, and a new zooming mode was added using Alt + Mouse Wheel.\n"
msgstr "Mode ubin jendela telah ditingkatkan dengan menyediakan dukungan untuk pengubinan-sudut, dan sebuah mode zum baru telah ditambahkan menggunakan Alt + Roda Tetikus.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Drag and drop a window to a corner to tile it][img-xfwm4-tiling-small]\n"
msgstr "![Seret dan jatuhkan sebuah jendela ke sudut untuk mengubinkannya][img-xfwm4-tiling-small]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "HiDPI Support"
msgstr "Dukungan HiDPI"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "In order to better support modern hi-resolution screens, two new Xfwm4 themes were added (hdpi, xhdpi).\n"
msgstr "Sebagai upaya untuk memberikan dukungan yang lebih baik terhadap layar modern beresolusi tinggi, dua tema Xfwm4 yang baru telah ditambahkan (hdpi, xhdpi).\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:41
#, no-wrap
msgid "Intelligent Hiding"
msgstr "Penyembunyian Pintar"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:44
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel can now intelligently hide itself when a window is dragged near it.\n"
msgstr "Panel kini dapat menyembunyikan dirinya secara cerdas ketika sebuah jendela diseret di dekatnya.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Oh what is this window??][img-panel-shown]\n"
msgstr "![Oh apakah jendela ini??][img-panel-shown]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Don't come closer!][img-panel-shown-stack]\n"
msgstr "![Jangan mendekat!][img-panel-shown-stack]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Hah! Now you don't see me!][img-panel-hidden]\n"
msgstr "![Hah! Sekarang kamu tidak melihatku!][img-panel-hidden]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:51
#, no-wrap
msgid "Gtk3 plugins"
msgstr "Plugin Gtk3"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:54
#, no-wrap
msgid "Infrastructure was added to be able to load Gtk3 plugins alongside Gtk2 plugins.\n"
msgstr "Infrastruktur ditambahkan agar bisa memuat plugin Gtk3 di samping plugin Gtk2.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:58
#, no-wrap
msgid "The desktop has a new wallpaper settings dialog with many new options and better multi-monitor support. Drag the dialog to the display or workspace where you want to change the wallpaper.\n"
msgstr "Desktop memiliki dialog pengaturan gambar latar belakang yang baru dengan beberapa opsi baru dan dukungan multi-monitor. Seret dialog ke tampilan atau ruang kerja di mana Anda ingin mengubah latar belakangnya.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Better multi-monitor support][img-xfdesktop-properties-multiworkspace]\n"
msgstr "![Dukungan yang lebih baik pada saat menggunakan banyak monitor][img-xfdesktop-properties-multiworkspace]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "Uncheck 'apply to all workspaces' to set a different wallpaper for each workspace.\n"
msgstr "Hilangkan tanda centang pada 'Terapkan ke semua ruang kerja' untuk menyetel latar belakang yang berbeda untuk tiap ruang kerja.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour412.md:63 content/about/tour410.md:63
#: content/about/tour48.md:73 content/about/tour46.md:85
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings *(xfce4-settings)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "Support for multi-monitor use was vastly improved in the display settings dialog. Upon connecting a new display, a quick setup popup offers some of the most-used modes for users to quickly change their layout.\n"
msgstr "Dukungan untuk penggunaan multi-monitor telah jauh meningkat pada dialog pengaturan tampilan. Ketika monitor baru terhubung, akan muncul sebuah penyiapan cepat yang menawarkan beberapa mode yang sering digunakan oleh pengguna untuk mengubah tata letak secara cepat.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:70
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Configure multiple displays][img-xfce4-display-settings-twoscreens]\n"
msgstr "![Konfigurasi multi-tampilan][img-xfce4-display-settings-twoscreens]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Choose your layout when plugging in a new display][img-xfce4-display-layout]\n"
msgstr "![Pilih tata letak Anda ketika memasang layar baru][img-xfce4-display-layout]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:76
#, no-wrap
msgid "The appearance dialog now showcases previews for styles and icons.\n"
msgstr "Dialog penampilan sekarang menampilkan pratinjau untuk gaya dan ikon.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Gtk style preview][img-xfce4-appearance-settings-style]\n"
msgstr "![Pratinjau gaya Gtk][img-xfce4-appearance-settings-style]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Icon theme preview][img-xfce4-appearance-settings-icons]\n"
msgstr "![Pratinjau tema ikon][img-xfce4-appearance-settings-icons]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:86
#, no-wrap
msgid "A new panel plugin was created which allows you to quickly control your screen brightness, either via the menu or by simply using your mouse's scroll wheel over the plugin. The plugin's menu also shows all other connected devices with a power status, e.g. bluetooth keyboards or wireless mice. It still offers quick access to the presentation mode, which inhibits your screensaver for as long as the option is active.\n"
msgstr "Sebuah plugin panel baru telah dibuat yang memungkinkan pengaturan kecerahan layar secara cepat, baik melalui menu maupun dengan menggulir roda tetikus di atas plugin tersebut. Menu plugin juga menampilkan semua perangkat lain yang terhubung, dengan sebuah status daya, misal papan tik bluetooth atau tetikus nirkabel. Ia masih menawarkan akses cepat ke mode presentasi, yang akan menonaktifkan penyimpan layar selama opsi ini aktif.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The plugin's menu allows users to control screen brightness and check on the remaining uptime their battery provides.][img-xfpm-plugin-crop]\n"
msgstr "![Menu plugin memungkinkan pengguna mengatur kecerahan layar dan melihat waktu hidup yang tersedia dari baterai.][img-xfpm-plugin-crop]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "The settings dialog was completely restructured (separating button/lid events from system and display behavior) and offers a clearer way of setting your preferences.\n"
msgstr "Dialog pengaturan telah direstrukturisasi secara lengkap (memisahkan even tombol/penutup laptop dari sistem dan perilaku tampilan) dan memberikan cara yang lebih jelas dalam menyetel preferensi Anda.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Configure what action to take when certain buttons are pressed or the laptop lid is closed][img-xfpm-prefs-general]\n"
msgstr "![Konfigurasi aksi yang akan diambil ketika tombol-tombol tertentu ditekan atau penutup laptop ditutup][img-xfpm-prefs-general]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:96
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Configure what to do when the user is inactive or battery is drained][img-xfpm-prefs-system]\n"
msgstr "![Konfigurasi apa yang harus dilakukan ketika pengguna tidak aktif atau baterai habis][img-xfpm-prefs-system]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:98
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Manage display power management][img-xfpm-prefs-display]\n"
msgstr "![Mengelola manajemen daya tampilan][img-xfpm-prefs-display]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:100
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Display information on all connected devices][img-xfpm-prefs-devices]\n"
msgstr "![Menampilkan informasi semua perangkat yang terhubung][img-xfpm-prefs-devices]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:102
#, no-wrap
msgid "When light-locker is available, you can control its settings directly via the power manager.\n"
msgstr "Ketika light-locker tersedia, Anda bisa mengatur setelannya secara langsung melalui manajer daya.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:104
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Setup light-locker integration][img-xfpm-prefs-security]\n"
msgstr "![Atur integrasi light-locker][img-xfpm-prefs-security]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:107
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tab Support"
msgstr "Dukungan Tab"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "A long-awaited feature was added: you can now open multiple folders in the same Thunar window.\n"
msgstr "Fitur yang lama ditunggu telah ditambahkan: Sekarang Anda bisa membuka beberapa folder di satu jendela Thunar.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:112
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Browse multiple directories][img-thunar-tabs]\n"
msgstr "![Meramban banyak direktori][img-thunar-tabs]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:114
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thunar now displays the remaining free space with a bar in a folder properties.\n"
msgstr "Thunar sekarang menampilkan sisa ruang kosong dengan tampilan bilah di properti folder.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:116
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Freespace bar][img-thunar-freespace]\n"
msgstr "![Bilah ruang kosong][img-thunar-freespace]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:118
#, no-wrap
msgid "And you can select multiple files to see their properties at once.\n"
msgstr "Dan Anda bis amemilih beberapa berkas untuk melihat propertinya dalam waktu yang bersamaan.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:120
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Multiple File Properties][img-thunar-multifiles-props]\n"
msgstr "![Properti Multi Berkas][img-thunar-multifiles-props]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour412.md:121
#, no-wrap
msgid "Goodies"
msgstr "Barang"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:124
#, no-wrap
msgid "There have been lots of improvements to our goodies, and some new and shiny applications have been added by new contributors.\n"
msgstr "Ada banyak peningkatan pada berbagai aplikasi kami, dan beberapa aplikasi baru telah ditambahkan oleh para kontributor baru.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:125
#, no-wrap
msgid "Alternative panel menu plugin *(xfce4-whiskermenu)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:128
#, no-wrap
msgid "The whisker menu is an alternative to the traditional menu plugin, showing favourites, allowing to search through existing apps and much more.\n"
msgstr "Menu Whisker adalah sebuah alternatif untuk plugin menu tradisional, menampilkan favorit, mampu melakukan pencarian aplikasi yang ada, dan lebih banyak lagi.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:130
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Browse through categories][img-whiskermenu-default]\n"
msgstr "![Menjelajahi kategori][img-whiskermenu-default]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:132
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Search for an application][img-whiskermenu-search]\n"
msgstr "![Mencari aplikasi][img-whiskermenu-search]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:133
#, no-wrap
msgid "Task Manager *(xfce4-taskmanager)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:136
#, no-wrap
msgid "The task manager got a revamped user interface, a filter and also supports Gtk3 now.\n"
msgstr "Manajer tugas mendapatkan perombakan antarmuka, sebuah penyaring, dan sekarang mendukung Gtk3.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:138
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Show processes as a tree][img-taskman-tree]\n"
msgstr "![Menampilkan proses secara bercabang][img-taskman-tree]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:140
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Filter processes by name][img-taskman-filter]\n"
msgstr "![Menyaring proses berdasarkan nama][img-taskman-filter]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:144
#, no-wrap
msgid "Parole's UI was totally redone in Gtk3. It now supports multiple video backends, makes more efficient use of your resources and contains a few novel plugins.\n"
msgstr "Antarmuka Parole telah dibangun ulang menggunakan Gtk3. Sekarang ia mendukung banyak backend video, menggunakan sumber daya komputer Anda secara lebih efisien dan memiliki beberapa plugin baru.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:146
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Watch videos][img-parole]\n"
msgstr "![Nonton video][img-parole]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:148
#, no-wrap
msgid "The media controls are now contained in a slide-over overlay (with a configurable timeout).\n"
msgstr "Pengontrol media sekarang diletakkan dalam sebuah lapisan meluncur (dengan batas waktu yang bisa diatur).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:150
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Listen to music][img-parole-audio]\n"
msgstr "![Mendengarkan musik][img-parole-audio]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:151
#, no-wrap
msgid "Text Editor *(mousepad)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:154
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mousepad was totally rewritten, gained a settings dialog and now supports Gtk3.\n"
msgstr "Mousepad telah ditulis ulang secara total, mendapatkan sebuah dialog pengaturan dan sekarang mendukung Gtk3.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:156
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New mousepad settings][img-mousepad-prefs]\n"
msgstr "![Pengaturan mousepad yang baru][img-mousepad-prefs]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour412.md:157
#, no-wrap
msgid "A note on Xfce's portability"
msgstr "Catatan terkait portabilitas Xfce"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:160
#, no-wrap
msgid "All but one of those screenshots were taken on machines running OpenBSD -current, a good proof that Xfce is still portable and friendly to all Unix systems.\n"
msgstr "Keseluruhan kecuali satu dari cuplikan layar tersebut diambil di mesin yang menjalankan OpenBSD -current, bukti yang bagus bahwa Xfce masih portabel dan ramah bagi semua sistem Unix.\n"

